## **Batch flags reference**

| Flag | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `WORKSPACE_ROOT` | Required â€” e.g. `F:\project_workspace` |
| `CONTAINER_ID` | Local Docker Postgres for export (auto-detect if omitted) |
| `/FORCE` | Skip local `Y/YES` prompt (does **not** skip remote `PRODUCTION`) |
| `/PROD` | Import `corrected_event_media_inserts.ordered_PROD.sql` |
| `/SKIP-EXPORT` | Skip steps 1â€“4; reuse existing `export.sql` / ordered / PROD files |
| `/REMOTE` | Steps 5â€“7 on RDS from `.env.local` (auto `/PROD`) |
| `/SCHEMA-ONLY` | Schema apply only (step 5) |
| `/DATA-ONLY` | Skip schema rebuild; import + sequences only |
| `/IMPORT-FILE "path"` | Custom SQL import (strict `ON_ERROR_STOP=1`) |
| `/REGEN-MOSC` | Regenerate `mosc_malankara_orthodox_2` tenant SQL |
| `/IMPORT-DUP-ONLY` | Fast MOSC tenant refresh via `mosc_dup_only.sql` |

Help: `database_export_import_refresh.bat --help`

