## **Pipeline steps (summary)**

| Step | Action | Output / target |
|------|--------|-----------------|
| 0 | Resolve Docker container | Local export source |
| 1 | `pg_dump --data-only --column-inserts` | `mosc-temp/code_html_template/SQLS/export.sql` |
| 2 | `node reorder_sql_inserts_final.cjs` | `corrected_event_media_inserts.ordered.sql` |
| 2b | `renumber_sql_insert_ids.cjs` + mojibake fix | `sequence_fix_inserts/corrected_event_media_inserts.renumbered.sql` |
| 3 | `node scripts/replace-user-profile-ids-in-sql.mjs` | `corrected_event_media_inserts.ordered_PROD.sql` |
| 4 | Comment `pg_dump` header lines in import file | Patched SQL |
| 5 | Apply `Latest_Schema_Post__Blob_Claude_12.sql` | Target DB schema |
| 6 | Import ordered / PROD / custom SQL | Target DB data |
| 7 | `sync_all_table_sequences.sql` + Spring Batch sync | Sequences |

